{"type":"message","id":"9e4aae98","parentId":"649c24c7","timestamp":"2026-03-13T11:43:46.988Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"用户问为什么设置了 `gateway.port: 12328`，但访问地址还是 `18789`。这是一个实际问题，我需要帮助排查。\n\n让我先查看用户的配置文件，确认 gateway.port 的设置，然后检查可能的原因。\n\n可能的原因：\n1. 配置文件没有正确保存或加载\n2. 有环境变量覆盖了配置（如 `OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT`）\n3. Gateway 没有重启，还在使用旧配置\n4. 有多个配置文件，加载了错误的那个\n5. 浏览器缓存或书签问题\n\n让我先查看用户的配置文件确认设置。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"function.read:70","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","limit":50,"offset":420}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773402190921}}
{"type":"message","id":"5bfd0292","parentId":"9e4aae98","timestamp":"2026-03-13T11:43:47.018Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"function.read:70","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"      \"memory_*\",\n      \"plugins.*\",\n      \"extensions.*\",\n      \"exec\",\n      \"process\",\n      \"sessions_*\"\n    ],\n    \"deny\": [\n      \"nodes.camera.snap\",\n      \"nodes.screen.record\",\n      \"bash\",\n      \"nodes.camera.stream\",\n      \"nodes.mic.record\",\n      \"nodes.speaker.play\"\n    ],\n    \"web\": {\n      \"search\": {\n        \"provider\": \"brave\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"BSAAg5L5kNDIJY9C0R4JrJcuKyRjfdo\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"elevated\": {\n      \"enabled\": true\n    }\n  },\n  \"broadcast\": {},\n  \"audio\": {},\n  \"messages\": {\n    \"responsePrefix\": \"🦞\",\n    \"groupChat\": {\n      \"mentionPatterns\": [\n        \"@openclaw\",\n        \"@助手\"\n      ],\n      \"historyLimit\": 50\n    },\n    \"queue\": {\n      \"mode\": \"collect\",\n      \"byChannel\": {\n        \"whatsapp\": \"collect\",\n        \"telegram\": \"collect\",\n        \"discord\": \"steer\"\n      },\n      \"debounceMs\": 1000,\n      \"cap\": 20,\n      \"drop\": \"summarize\"\n    },\n    \"inbound\": {\n      \"debounceMs\": 2000,\n      \"byChannel\": {\n\n[125 more lines in file. Use offset=470 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773402227009}}
