{"type":"message","id":"16686db0","parentId":"0fb77fc4","timestamp":"2026-03-13T11:44:37.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问了一个实际问题：为什么配置文件中设置了 gateway.port: 12328，但访问时还是 18789 端口。\n\n我需要帮用户排查这个问题。根据 OpenClaw 的文档，端口优先级是：\n1. --port 命令行参数（最高）\n2. OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT 环境变量\n3. CLAWDBOT_GATEWAY_PORT 环境变量\n4. gateway.port 配置项\n5. 默认 18789（最低）\n\n我已经确认用户的配置文件中确实有 \"port\": 12328，所以问题可能是：\n1. 环境变量覆盖了配置\n2. Gateway 没有重启\n3. 命令行参数覆盖\n4. 浏览器缓存/书签问题\n\n让我给用户一个清晰的排查指南。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我确认了你的配置文件中确实设置了 `\"port\": 12328`。问题出在 **OpenClaw 的端口优先级规则**。\n\n## 🔍 端口优先级（从高到低）\n\n```\n1. --port 命令行参数           ← 最高优先级\n2. OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT 环境变量\n3. CLAWDBOT_GATEWAY_PORT 环境变量\n4. gateway.port 配置项          ← 你设置的在这里\n5. 默认 18789                   ← 最低优先级\n```\n\n**环境变量或命令行参数会覆盖你的配置文件设置！**\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 排查步骤\n\n### 1️⃣ 检查环境变量（最可能的原因）\n\n在 PowerShell 中运行：\n```powershell\necho $env:OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT\necho $env:CLAWDBOT_GATEWAY_PORT\n```\n\n如果输出了 `18789`，说明**环境变量覆盖了配置**。\n\n### 2️⃣ 检查 Gateway 是否已重启\n\n配置修改后需要重启 Gateway：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 3️⃣ 检查实际运行端口\n\n```bash\nopenclaw status\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 解决方案\n\n**方案 A：删除环境变量（推荐）**\n```powershell\nRemove-Item Env:\\OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nRemove-Item Env:\\CLAWDBOT_GATEWAY_PORT -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n**方案 B：修改环境变量**\n```powershell\n$env:OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=\"12328\"\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n**方案 C：直接用命令行启动**\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway --port 12328\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 验证\n\n重启后访问：\n- ✅ `http://127.0.0.1:12328` — 应该能访问\n- ❌ `http://127.0.0.1:18789` — 应该无法访问\n\n**我猜你的系统环境变量里有 `OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=18789`！** 🔍"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopRe