{"type":"message","id":"122752b9","parentId":"ea72f9dd","timestamp":"2026-03-13T11:50:39.696Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-03-13 19:50 GMT+8] OpenClaw status\n\nOverview\n┌─────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│ Item │ Value │\n├─────────────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Dashboard │ http://127.0.0.1:12328/ │\n│ OS │ windows 10.0.19045 (x64) · node 24.9.0\n这里的端口好像是生效了，webUI的端口怎么调整"}],"timestamp":1773402639686}}
{"type":"message","id":"35966b00","parentId":"122752b9","timestamp":"2026-03-13T11:51:03.466Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是 WebUI 的端口怎么调整。根据我之前读取的配置文档，Control UI 的端口是跟 Gateway 端口绑定的，Control UI 没有独立的端口配置，它运行在 Gateway 的同一个端口上。\n\n让我回顾一下配置文档中关于 Control UI 的部分：\n\n```json5\n{\n  gateway: {\n    controlUi: {\n      enabled: true,\n      basePath: \"/openclaw\",\n      // root: \"dist/control-ui\",\n      // allowedOrigins: [\"https://control.example.com\"],\n      // dangerouslyAllowHostHeaderOriginFallback: false,\n      // allowInsecureAuth: false,\n      // dangerouslyDisableDeviceAuth: false,\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\nControl UI 是运行在 Gateway 端口上的，没有独立的端口配置。用户看到的 Dashboard URL `http://127.0.0.1:12328/` 就是 Gateway + Control UI 的地址。\n\n但用户可能问的是：\n1. Control UI 的 basePath（路径前缀）\n2. 或者用户以为有独立的 WebUI 端口\n\n让我解释清楚 Control UI 的配置方式。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据 `openclaw status` 输出，**Gateway 端口 12328 已经生效了**！✅\n\n---\n\n## 🎛️ Control UI 端口配置\n\nControl UI **没有独立的端口**，它运行在 **Gateway 的同一个端口**上。\n\n你看到的 `http://127.0.0.1:12328/` 就是 Control UI 的地址。\n\n---\n\n## 📍 Control UI 路径配置\n\n如果你想调整 Control UI 的 **访问路径**（不是端口），可以配置 `basePath`：\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"port\": 12328,\n    \"controlUi\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"basePath\": \"/openclaw\"  // ← 访问路径前缀\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n| basePath | 访问地址 |\n|----------|----------|\n| `\"/openclaw\"` (默认) | `http://127.0.0.1:12328/openclaw` |\n| `\"/\"` | `http://127.0.0.1:12328/` |\n| `\"/dashboard\"` | `http://127.0.0.1:12328/dashboard` |\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 你的当前配置\n\n让我检查一下你当前的 Control UI 配置：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bd80cec7a9da4d248da7259b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","limit":30,"offset":540}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,