{"type":"message","id":"fa1a87e4","parentId":"c448a221","timestamp":"2026-03-13T11:51:29.097Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户的 gateway 配置中没有设置 `controlUi`，所以会使用默认值。根据文档，默认的 basePath 是 `/openclaw`，但用户 status 输出显示的是 `http://127.0.0.1:12328/`（根路径）。\n\n让我给用户解释 Control UI 的配置方式。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你的配置中没有设置 `controlUi`，会使用默认值。\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 当前状态\n\n| 项目 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| Gateway 端口 | `12328` ✅ |\n| Control UI 端口 | 同 Gateway (`12328`) |\n| Control UI 路径 | 默认 `/` (根路径) |\n\n**访问地址：** `http://127.0.0.1:12328/`\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 如果你想调整\n\n```json5\n{\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"port\": 12328,\n    \"controlUi\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"basePath\": \"/openclaw\"  // 改为 /openclaw\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n修改后重启：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n**你具体想调整成什么？** 🤔"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773402663483}}
