{"type":"message","id":"796a6d68","parentId":"35c054b8","timestamp":"2026-03-13T12:59:15.792Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"子代理搜索失败了，但我可以直接读取已知的文档路径来给用户展示完整的配置参考。让我直接读取 configuration-reference.md 文件，这是最完整的配置文档。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4ea19cf0eb224f88bffc2bad","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\gateway\\configuration-reference.md","limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773406736841}}
{"type":"message","id":"25946715","parentId":"796a6d68","timestamp":"2026-03-13T12:59:15.821Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4ea19cf0eb224f88bffc2bad","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\ntitle: \"Configuration Reference\"\ndescription: \"Complete field-by-field reference for ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\"\nsummary: \"Complete reference for every OpenClaw config key, defaults, and channel settings\"\nread_when:\n  - You need exact field-level config semantics or defaults\n  - You are validating channel, model, gateway, or tool config blocks\n---\n\n# Configuration Reference\n\nEvery field available in `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`. For a task-oriented overview, see [Configuration](/gateway/configuration).\n\nConfig format is **JSON5** (comments + trailing commas allowed). All fields are optional — OpenClaw uses safe defaults when omitted.\n\n---\n\n## Channels\n\nEach channel starts automatically when its config section exists (unless `enabled: false`).\n\n### DM and group access\n\nAll channels support DM policies and group policies:\n\n| DM policy           | Behavior                                                        |\n| ------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| `pairing` (default) | Unknown senders get a one-time pairing code; owner must approve |\n| `allowlist`         | Only senders in `allowFrom` (or paired allow store)             |\n| `open`              | Allow all inbound DMs (requires `allowFrom: [\"*\"]`)             |\n| `disabled`          | Ignore all inbound DMs                                          |\n\n| Group policy          | Behavior                                               |\n| --------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------ |\n| `allowlist` (default) | Only groups matching the configured allowlist          |\n| `open`                | Bypass group allowlists (mention-gating still applies) |\n| `disabled`            | Block all group/room messages                          |\n\n<Note>\n`channels.defaults.groupPolicy` sets the default when a provider's `groupPolicy` is unset.\nPairing codes expire after 1 hour. Pending DM pairing requests are capped at **3 per channel**.\nIf a provider block is missing entirely (`channels.<provider>` absent), runtime group policy falls back to `allowlist` (fail-closed) with a startup warning.\n</Note>\n\n### Channel model overrides\n\nUse `channels.modelByChannel` to pin specific channel IDs to a model. Values accept `provider/model` or configured model aliases. The channel mapping applies when a session does not already have a model override (for example, set via `/model`).\n\n```json5\n{\n  channels: {\n    modelByChannel: {\n      discord: {\n        \"123456789012345678\": \"anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\",\n      },\n      slack: {\n        C1234567890: \"openai/gpt-4.1\",\n      },\n      telegram: {\n        \"-1001234567890\": \"openai/gpt-4.1-mini\",\n        \"-1001234567890:topic:99\": \"anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6\",\n      },\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\n### Channel defaults and heartbeat\n\nUse `channels.defaults` for shared group-policy and heartbeat behavior across providers:\n\n```json5\n{\n  channels: {\n    defaults: {\n      groupPolicy: \"allowlist\", // open | allowlist | disabled\n      heartbeat: {\n        showOk: false,\n        showAlerts: true,\n        useIndicator: true,\n      },\n    },\n  },\n}\n```\n\n- `channels.defaults.groupPolicy`: fallback group policy when a provider-level `groupPolicy` is unset.\n- `channels.defaults.heartbeat.showOk`: include healthy channel statuses in heartbeat output.\n- `channels.defaults.heartbeat.showAlerts`: include degraded/error statuses in heartbeat output.\n- `channels.defaults.heartbeat.useIndicator`: render compact indicator-style heartbeat output.\n\n### WhatsApp\n\nWhatsApp runs through the gateway's web channel (Baileys Web). It starts automatically when a linked session exists.\n\n```json5\n{\n  channels: {\n    whatsapp: {\n      dmPolicy: \"pairing\", // pairing | allowlist | open | disabled\n\n[2882 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773406755813}}
{"type":"message","id":"3a1cac13","parentId":"25946715","timestamp":"2026-03-13T12:59:26.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我找到了完整的配置参考文档。现在让我给用户一个完整的总结，告诉他所有可用的配置资源。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"完美！我找到了完整的配置文档。以下是**所有 OpenClaw 配置资源的完整列表**：\n\n---\n\n## 📚 完整配置文档列表\n\n### 1. 核心配置文档\n\n| 文档 | 本地路径 | 说明 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| **Configuration Reference** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\gateway\\configuration-reference.md` | ⭐ **最完整**，3000+ 行，所有配置项 |\n| **Configuration** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\gateway\\configuration.md` | 面向任务的配置指南 |\n\n### 2. 专项配置文档\n\n| 主题 | 本地路径 |\n|------|----------|\n| **Channels（渠道配置）** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\channels\\` |\n| **Tools（工具配置）** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\tools\\` |\n| **Agents（Agent 配置）** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\concepts\\agent.md` |\n| **Models（模型配置）** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\concepts\\models.md` |\n| **Session（会话配置）** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\concepts\\session.md` |\n| **Sandbox（沙箱配置）** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\gateway\\sandboxing.md` |\n| **Security（安全配置）** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\gateway\\security.md` |\n| **Secrets（密钥管理）** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\gateway\\secrets.md` |\n| **Hooks（Webhook 配置）** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\automation\\webhook.md` |\n| **Cron（定时任务）** | `F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\automation\\cron-jobs.md` |\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ CLI 配置命令\n\n```bash\n# 查看配置\nopenclaw config get                          # 查看所有配置\nopenclaw config get gateway.port             # 查看特定配置项\n\n# 修改配置\nopenclaw config set gateway.port 12328       # 设置配置项\nopenclaw config unset gateway.tls.enabled    # 删除配置项\n\n# 验证配置\nopenclaw config validate                     # 验证配置是否有效\nopenclaw doctor                              # 检查配置问题并修复\n\n# 配置编辑器（交互式）\nopenclaw configure                           # 配置向导\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🌐 在线文档\n\n| 资源 | 地址 |\n|------|------|\n| **完整配置参考** | https://docs.openclaw.ai/gateway/configuration-reference |\n| **配置指南** | https://docs.openclaw.ai/gateway/configuration |\n| **所有文档** | https://docs.openclaw.ai |\n| **GitHub 源码** | https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw |\n| **技能市场** | https://clawhub.com |\n\n---\n\n## 💻 代码中的 Schema（高级）\n\n配置 Schema 定义在源码中，但**已编译到 dist 目录**，阅读文档更友好：\n\n```\nF:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\\n├── docs/gateway/configuration-reference.md  ← 📖 读这个！\n├── src/config/                               ← 源码配置逻辑\n└── dist/*.js                                 ← 编译后的代码（含 Schema 验证）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📋 快速查找配置项\n\n在 PowerShell 中搜索配置：\n\n```powershell\n# 在文档中搜索配置关键字\nSelect-String -Path \"F:\\Program\\nvm\\node_global\\node_modules\\openclaw\\docs\\**\\*.md\" -Pattern \"broadcast|backup|monitoring\" -MaxCount 20\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 推荐用法\n\n1. **日常查询** → 读 `configuration-reference.md`\n2. **修改配置** → 用 `openclaw config set` 命令\n3. **验证配置** → 用 `openclaw doctor`\n4. **在线查阅** → https://docs.openclaw.ai\n\n**最完整的配置文档就是这个 3000+ 行的 `configuration-reference.md`！** 📖"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773406755819}}
