{"type":"message","id":"d26ed6c5","parentId":"2392ed6c","timestamp":"2026-03-13T14:54:21.266Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户报告了一个配置验证错误，说 tools.allow 列表中包含了一些未知的工具条目。我需要查看当前的配置并修复它，使用正确的工具名称。\n\n根据我之前看到的文档，OpenClaw 的工具组包括：\n- group:fs → read, write, edit, apply_patch\n- group:runtime → exec, process\n- group:sessions → sessions_list, sessions_history, sessions_send, sessions_spawn, session_status\n- group:memory → memory_search, memory_get\n- group:web → web_search, web_fetch\n- group:ui → browser, canvas\n- group:automation → cron, gateway\n- group:messaging → message\n- group:nodes → nodes\n\n报错的工具名称格式不对，比如：\n- trash → 可能是 write 的一部分\n- list → 可能是 read 或 sessions_list\n- mkdir → 可能是 write 的一部分\n- copy, move → 可能是 write 的一部分\n- web.search → 应该是 web_search\n- fetch → 应该是 web_fetch\n- http → 可能是 http 工具\n- images → 应该是 image\n- draw → 可能是 draw 工具\n- memory_* → 应该是 memory_search, memory_get\n- plugins.* → 插件工具\n- extensions.* → 扩展工具\n- sessions_* → 应该是 sessions_list, sessions_history, sessions_send, sessions_spawn, session_status\n\n让我先读取当前配置，然后修复它。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这个错误是因为 `tools.allow` 列表中使用了**错误的工具名称格式**。让我帮你修复：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_123c215d65b842a0a684271f","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","limit":50,"offset":400}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773413649717}}
