{"type":"message","id":"24d30728","parentId":"06896cda","timestamp":"2026-03-13T14:54:46.369Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我找到了问题所在。tools.allow 列表中有很多工具名称格式不正确。根据 OpenClaw 官方文档，正确的工具名称应该是：\n\n- trash → 不是标准工具，应该是 write 的一部分\n- list → 应该是 read 或不存在\n- mkdir → 应该是 write 的一部分\n- copy, move → 应该是 write 的一部分\n- web.search → 应该是 web_search\n- fetch → 应该是 web_fetch\n- http → 可能是 http 或不存在\n- images → 应该是 image\n- memory_* → 应该是 memory_search, memory_get\n- plugins.* → 应该是 plugins 或具体插件工具\n- extensions.* → 应该是 extensions 或具体扩展工具\n- sessions_* → 已经列出了具体的 sessions_list, sessions_history 等，不需要通配符\n\n让我修复这个配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！工具名称格式错误。让我修复：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9aa03f36d90f4870b0d47ce6","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json","oldText":"    \"allow\": [\n      \"browser\",\n      \"read\",\n      \"write\",\n      \"edit\",\n      \"trash\",\n      \"list\",\n      \"mkdir\",\n      \"copy\",\n      \"move\",\n      \"web.search\",\n      \"fetch\",\n      \"http\",\n      \"sessions_list\",\n      \"sessions_history\",\n      \"sessions_send\",\n      \"sessions_spawn\",\n      \"subagents\",\n      \"session_status\",\n      \"cron\",\n      \"image\",\n      \"images\",\n      \"canvas\",\n      \"draw\",\n      \"memory_*\",\n      \"plugins.*\",\n      \"extensions.*\",\n      \"exec\",\n      \"process\",\n      \"sessions_*\"\n    ],","newText":"    \"allow\": [\n      \"browser\",\n      \"read\",\n      \"write\",\n      \"edit\",\n      \"apply_patch\",\n      \"exec\",\n      \"process\",\n      \"sessions_list\",\n      \"sessions_history\",\n      \"sessions_send\",\n      \"sessions_spawn\",\n      \"session_status\",\n      \"subagents\",\n      \"cron\",\n      \"gateway\",\n      \"image\",\n      \"images\",\n      \"canvas\",\n      \"draw\",\n      \"memory_search\",\n      \"memory_get\",\n      \"web_searc