{"type":"message","id":"a3a7a4b2","parentId":"a4100dc1","timestamp":"2026-03-13T15:01:07.882Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要搭建一个 agent 团队，需要最简单的方案。根据我之前对 OpenClaw 配置的了解，最简单的方式是使用 `agents.list` 配置多个 Agent，然后通过 `bindings` 进行路由。\n\n让我给出一个最简化的配置方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！给你 **OpenClaw Agent 团队最简单方案**：\n\n---\n\n## 🤖 最简单 Agent 团队方案\n\n### 方案：多 Agent 配置（无需额外插件）\n\n**只需修改 `openclaw.json`，添加 2-3 个 Agent 即可。**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 完整配置示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"ceo\",\n        \"name\": \"CEO Agent\",\n        \"default\": true,\n        \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-ceo\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3-max-2026-01-23\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"CEO\",\n          \"theme\": \"executive leader\",\n          \"emoji\": \"👔\",\n          \"avatar\": \"avatar/ceo.jpg\"\n        },\n        \"groupChat\": {\n          \"mentionPatterns\": [\"@CEO\", \"@老板\"]\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"dev\",\n        \"name\": \"Developer Agent\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-dev\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"DevBot\",\n          \"theme\": \"professional\",\n          \"emoji\": \"💻\",\n          \"avatar\": \"avatar/dev.jpg\"\n        },\n        \"groupChat\": {\n          \"mentionPatterns\": [\"@Dev\", \"@开发\"]\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"assistant\",\n        \"name\": \"Assistant Agent\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-assistant\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"dashscope-coding/qwen3.5-plus\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"小助手\",\n          \"theme\": \"helpful assistant\",\n          \"emoji\": \"🤖\",\n          \"avatar\": \"avatar/assistant.jpg\"\n        },\n        \"groupChat\": {\n          \"mentionPatterns\": [\"@助手\", \"@help\"]\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"bindings\": [\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"ceo\",\n      \"match\": { \"channel\": \"whatsapp\", \"accountId\": \"ceo\" }\n    },\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"dev\",\n      \"match\": { \"channel\": \"whatsapp\", \"accountId\": \"dev\" }\n    },\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"assistant\",\n      \"match\": { \"channel\": \"whatsapp\", \"accountId\": \"assistant\" }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 最简化版本（3 个 Agent）\n\n| Agent | 用途 | 模型 | Emoji |\n|-------|------|------|-------|\n| **CEO** | 决策、管理 | qwen3-max | 👔 |\n| **Dev** | 编程、技术 | qwen3.5-plus | 💻 |\n| **Assistant** | 日常任务 | qwen3.5-plus | 🤖 |\n\n---\n\n## 📁 目录结构\n\n```\nC:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\\n├── openclaw.json              # 主配置\n├── workspace-ceo/             # CEO 工作区\n│   ├── avatar/ceo.jpg\n│   ├── SOUL.md\n│   └── memory/\n├── workspace-dev/             # 开发工作区\n│   ├── avatar/dev.jpg\n│   ├── SOUL.md\n│   └── memory/\n└── workspace-assistant/       # 助手工作区\n    ├── avatar/assistant.jpg\n    ├── SOUL.md\n    └── memory/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 快速搭建步骤\n\n### 1️⃣ 创建工作区目录\n\n```powershell\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path \"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\workspace-ceo\\avatar\" -Force\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path \"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\workspace-dev\\avatar\" -Force\nNew-Item -ItemType Directory -Path \"C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\workspace-assistant\\avatar\" -Force\n```\n\n### 2️⃣ 放入头像图片\n\n准备 3 张头像图片：\n- `ceo.jpg` → `workspace-ceo/avatar/`\n- `dev.jpg` → `workspace-dev/avatar/`\n- `assistant.jpg` → `workspace-assistant/avatar/`\n\n### 3️⃣ 修改配置\n\n编辑 `C:\\Users\\28964\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json`，添加上面的 `agents.list` 和 `bindings` 配置。\n\n### 4️⃣ 重启 Gateway\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n## 💬 使用方式\n\n### 场景 1：私聊（每个 Agent 独立）\n\n```\nWhatsApp 账号 1 (+86-CEO) → CEO Agent\nWhatsApp 账号 2 (+86-DEV) → Dev Agent\nWhatsApp 账号 3 (+86-ASST) → Assistant Agent\n```\n\n### 场景 2：群聊（通过 @ 提及）\n\n```\n群聊消息：@CEO 这个项目怎么做？\n→ CEO Agent 回复\n\n群聊消息：@Dev 帮我写个函数\n→ Dev Agent 回复\n\n群聊消息：@助手 查一下天气\n→ Assistant Agent 回复\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 最简化配置（仅修改这部分）\n\n**你只需要在现有配置中添加：**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"ceo\",\n        \"name\": \"CEO Agent\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-ceo\",\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"CEO\",\n          \"theme\": \"executive leader\",\n          \"emoji\": \"👔\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"dev\",\n        \"name\": \"Developer Agent\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-dev\",\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"DevBot\",\n          \"theme\": \"professional\",\n          \"emoji\": \"💻\"\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**就这 20 行代码，就能创建 2 个独立 Agent！**\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 总结\n\n| 步骤 | 操作 | 时间 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 1 | 创建工作区目录 | 1 分钟 |\n| 2 | 放入头像图片 | 1 分钟 |\n| 3 | 修改配置 | 5 分钟 |\n| 4 | 重启 Gateway | 30 秒 |\n\n**总共 10 分钟内搞定！** 🚀\n\n需要我帮你生成完整的配置文件吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773414035616}}
