{"type":"message","id":"9e58fe71","parentId":"dd380feb","timestamp":"2026-03-13T15:04:49.036Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"子代理搜索没有返回结果，但我已经通过阅读官方文档获取了足够的信息。现在给用户总结最佳方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据我查阅的 OpenClaw 官方文档，给你总结**最佳方案**：\n\n---\n\n## 🏆 OpenClaw Agent 团队最佳方案\n\n### ✅ 方案对比\n\n| 方案 | 难度 | 时间 | 推荐度 |\n|------|------|------|--------|\n| **CLI 向导** | ⭐ | 5 分钟 | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **GitHub 模板** | ⭐⭐ | 10 分钟 | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |\n| **手动配置** | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ | 30 分钟 | ⭐⭐ |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 推荐：使用 CLI 向导（最简单）\n\n```bash\n# 1. 创建 Agent 团队\nopenclaw agents add ceo\nopenclaw agents add dev\nopenclaw agents add assistant\n\n# 2. 验证\nopenclaw agents list --bindings\n\n# 3. 重启\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n**向导会自动：**\n- ✅ 创建工作区目录\n- ✅ 创建 `SOUL.md`、`AGENTS.md`、`USER.md`\n- ✅ 配置独立会话存储\n- ✅ 提示配置 bindings\n\n---\n\n## 📁 自动创建的目录结构\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/\n├── agents/\n│   ├── ceo/\n│   │   ├── agent/          # 认证、模型配置\n│   │   └── sessions/       # 会话历史\n│   ├── dev/\n│   │   ├── agent/\n│   │   └── sessions/\n│   └── assistant/\n│       ├── agent/\n│       └── sessions/\n├── workspace-ceo/\n│   ├── SOUL.md\n│   ├── AGENTS.md\n│   ├── USER.md\n│   └── avatar/\n├── workspace-dev/\n│   └── ...\n└── workspace-assistant/\n    └── ...\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔗 官方资源\n\n| 资源 | 地址 |\n|------|------|\n| **多 Agent 文档** | https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/multi-agent |\n| **配置参考** | https://docs.openclaw.ai/gateway/configuration-reference |\n| **GitHub 示例** | https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/tree/main/examples |\n| **ClawHub 插件** | https://clawhub.com |\n\n---\n\n## 💡 高级用法（可选）\n\n### 单 WhatsApp 账号多用户\n\n```json\n{\n  \"bindings\": [\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"ceo\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n        \"peer\": { \"kind\": \"direct\", \"id\": \"+86-13800138001\" }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"agentId\": \"dev\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n        \"peer\": { \"kind\": \"direct\", \"id\": \"+86-13800138002\" }\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**一个 WhatsApp 号码，不同联系人私聊自动路由到不同 Agent！**\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 总结\n\n**最简单的方案：**\n\n```bash\nopenclaw agents add ceo\nopenclaw agents add dev\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n**5 分钟搞定 Agent 团队！** 🚀\n\n**需要我帮你执行这些命令吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773414266077}}
