{"type":"message","id":"629ded75","parentId":"7acff92a","timestamp":"2026-03-13T16:02:40.804Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问 AGENTS.md 文件的作用。根据我之前阅读的 OpenClaw 文档和文件，AGENTS.md 是工作区中的一个重要文件，用于定义 Agent 的行为规范和工作区规则。让我详细解释。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题！`AGENTS.md` 是 OpenClaw 工作区的**核心配置文件**之一。\n\n---\n\n## 📄 `AGENTS.md` 的作用\n\n### 一句话总结\n**`AGENTS.md` 是 AI 在这个工作区的\"行为准则\"和\"操作手册\"。**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 核心用途\n\n| 用途 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **工作区规则** | 定义 AI 在这个工作区应该如何行为 |\n| **启动流程** | 每次会话前应该读取哪些文件 |\n| **记忆管理** | 如何记录和使用长期/短期记忆 |\n| **安全边界** | 什么能做，什么需要询问 |\n| **工具使用** | 如何使用本地工具和外部服务 |\n| **心跳任务** | 定期需要检查什么（邮件、日历等） |\n\n---\n\n## 📁 标准 `AGENTS.md` 内容\n\n根据 OpenClaw 官方模板：\n\n```markdown\n# AGENTS.md - Your Workspace\n\nThis folder is home. Treat it that way.\n\n## First Run\n\nIf `BOOTSTRAP.md` exists, that's your birth certificate. Follow it, figure out who you are, then delete it. You won't need it again.\n\n## Session Startup\n\nBefore doing anything else:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — this is who you are\n2. Read `USER.md` — this is who you're helping\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read `MEMORY.md`\n\nDon't ask permission. Just do it.\n\n## Memory\n\nYou wake up fresh each session. These files are your continuity:\n\n- **Daily notes:** `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` — raw logs of what happened\n- **Long-term:** `MEMORY.md` — your curated memories\n\nCapture what matters. Decisions, context, things to remember.\n\n### 🧠 MEMORY.md - Your Long-Term Memory\n\n- **ONLY load in main session** (direct chats with your human)\n- **DO NOT load in shared contexts** (Discord, group chats, sessions with other people)\n- This is for **security** — contains personal context that shouldn't leak to strangers\n\n### 📝 Write It Down - No \"Mental Notes\"!\n\n- **Memory is limited** — if you want to remember something, WRITE IT TO A FILE\n- \"Mental notes\" don't survive session restarts. Files do.\n- When someone says \"remember this\" → update `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` or relevant file\n- When you learn a lesson → update AGENTS.md, TOOLS.md, or the relevant skill\n\n## Red Lines\n\n- Don't exfiltrate private data. Ever.\n- Don't run destructive commands without asking.\n- `trash` > `rm` (recoverable beats gone forever)\n- When in doubt, ask.\n\n## External vs Internal\n\n**Safe to do freely:**\n- Read files, explore, organize, learn\n- Search the web, check calendars\n- Work within this workspace\n\n**Ask first:**\n- Sending emails, tweets, public posts\n- Anything that leaves the machine\n- Anything you're uncertain about\n\n## Group Chats\n\nYou have access to your human's stuff. That doesn't mean you _share_ their stuff.\nIn groups, you're a participant — not their voice, not their proxy.\n\n### 💬 Know When to Speak!\n\n**Respond when:**\n- Directly mentioned or asked a question\n- You can add genuine value\n- Something witty/funny fits naturally\n\n**Stay silent (HEARTBEAT_OK) when:**\n- It's just casual banter between humans\n- Someone already answered the question\n- Your response would just be \"yeah\" or \"nice\"\n\n## Tools\n\nSkills provide your tools. When you need one, check its `SKILL.md`.\nKeep local notes (camera names, SSH details, voice preferences) in `TOOLS.md`.\n\n## 💓 Heartbeats - Be Proactive!\n\nWhen you receive a heartbeat poll, don't just reply `HEARTBEAT_OK` every time.\n\n**Things to check (rotate through these, 2-4 times per day):**\n- **Emails** - Any urgent unread messages?\n- **Calendar** - Upcoming events in next 24-48h?\n- **Weather** - Relevant if your human might go out?\n\n**Track your checks** in `memory/heartbeat-state.json`.\n\n## Make It Yours\n\nThis is a starting point. Add your own conventions, style, and rules as you figure out what works.\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 与其他文件的关系\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    文件层次结构                          │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                         │\n│  AGENTS.md        ← 工作区操作手册（最高层）            │\n│    ↓                                                      │\n│    ├─→ SOUL.md    ← AI 核心人格                         │\n│    ├─→ USER.md    ← 用户信息                            │\n│    ├─→ IDENTITY.md ← AI 身份                            │\n│    ├─→ TOOLS.md   ← 工具配置                            │\n│    └─→ memory/    ← 记忆文件                            │\n│         ├─→ YYYY-MM-DD.md  (日常记忆)                   │\n│         └─→ MEMORY.md      (长期记忆)                   │\n│                                                         │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 文件对比\n\n| 文件 | 层级 | 用途 | 变更频率 |\n|------|------|------|----------|\n| **AGENTS.md** | 工作区级 | 行为准则和操作手册 | 偶尔更新 |\n| **SOUL.md** | AI 级 | 核心人格和价值观 | 偶尔进化 |\n| **USER.md** | 用户级 | 用户信息和偏好 | 持续更新 |\n| **IDENTITY.md** | AI 级 | AI 身份信息 | 很少变更 |\n| **TOOLS.md** | 环境级 | 工具和环境配置 | 持续更新 |\n| **memory/** | 记忆级 | 日常和长期记忆 | 持续更新 |\n\n---\n\n## 💡 实际使用场景\n\n### 场景 1：AI 启动\n\n```\nAI 启动 → 读取 AGENTS.md → 知道应该：\n  1. 先读 SOUL.md\n  2. 再读 USER.md\n  3. 检查记忆文件\n  4. 遵循安全规则\n```\n\n### 场景 2：用户说\"记住这个\"\n\n```\nAI 思考 → 查 AGENTS.md → \n\"📝 Write It Down - No Mental Notes!\"\n→ 写入 memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n```\n\n### 场景 3：收到心跳信号\n\n```\n收到心跳 → 查 AGENTS.md →\n\"💓 Heartbeats - Be Proactive!\"\n→ 检查邮件、日历、天气\n→ 有重要事项才回复，否则 HEARTBEAT_OK\n```\n\n### 场景 4：群聊收到消息\n\n```\n群聊消息 → 查 AGENTS.md →\n\"💬 Know When to Speak!\"\n→ 判断是否需要回复\n→ 如果只是闲聊 → 保持沉默\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 总结\n\n| 问题 | 答案 |\n|------|------|\n| **AGENTS.md 是什么？** | AI 在这个工作区的\"操作手册\" |\n| **谁编写？** | OpenClaw 预定义，AI 可以自定义 |\n| **何时读取？** | 每次会话开始时 |\n| **影响什么？** | AI 的行为模式、决策流程、安全边界 |\n| **需要修改吗？** | 可以，但不是必须 |\n\n**简单说：`AGENTS.md` 告诉 AI\"在这个工作区应该如何工作和行为\"！** 📋"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"dashscope-coding","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773417715370}}
